  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    RDKitMolFragmenterNodeDialog
    The dialog to configure the RDKit node.
    RDKitMolFragmenterNodeFactory
    NodeFactory for the RDKit based "RDKitMolFragmenter" Node.
    RDKitMolFragmenterNodeModel
    This class implements the node model of the "RDKitMolFragmenter" node providing fragment calculations for RDKit Molecules based on the open source RDKit library.
